summary: TL*THE CONTACT OWNS A 2007 HONDA GOLDWING (NA).  WHILE DRIVING AT VARIOUS SPEEDS ON A SUNNY DAY, THE CONTACT SEES A RAINBOW OF COLORS ACROSS THE WINDSHIELD.  THE VEHICLE WAS TAKEN TO THE DEALER ONCE AND THE WINDSHIELD WAS REPLACED.  THE CONTACT CONTINUES TO SEE THE RAINBOW OF COLORS ACROSS THE WINDSHIELD.   THE CURRENT MILEAGE WAS 7,000 AND FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 10.   UPDATED 03-04-08 *BF
